Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to activate this card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:01:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Darkness Within Yugi - \NTimaeus Disappears"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obtain the power of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Attack Power rises by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because her Attack Strength has now changed, the Crystal Seal is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Timaeus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Orichalcos and the power of the Legendary Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other terminology, the very powers of light and darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cannot coexist together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the source of my uneasiness is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still have the power to Summon up to ten Monsters with increased Attack Power onto the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Barrier of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if this is a trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only use this power to continue fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card known\N as Hand Control!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand Control is a card that allows one to declare the name of a card in the opponent's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can then forcefully activate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the card you are after is the Necromancy I now hold in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it then, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of Necromancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four Monsters in my Graveyard are Summoned back to the field in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Berfomet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion Beast Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I sacrifice Gazelle and Berfomet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, the Special Effect of Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Undo the combination, Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters, take in the powers of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the power of Orichalcos,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ATK of each Kuriboh increases by 500 points too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I activate the Special Effect of Kuriba!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself again, Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Attack Power of Kuribabylon is decided by the total Attack Points of the Kuribohs used to form it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Kuribabylon itself can also take in the power of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So its ATK is now 4500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 4500 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazin' array a' powerful Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he Summoned them all in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, a card like The Barrier of Orichalcos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is really a powerful card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of Orichalcos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is {\i1}your{\i0} power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Kay'est is a Monster that cannot be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, Kuribabylon, attack Guardian Grarl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Grarl...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you have a Monster in your Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the continuous effect of Purity of the Cemetery is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Black Magician and Black Magician Girl have yet to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quickplay Magic, Divine Protection of the Deceased!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine Protection of the Deceased is a card that, when my Monster gets destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allows me to discard two cards from my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the opponent's turn, I can activate this card to negate the Battle Phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would Yugi have the mark of Orichalcos on his forehead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys came too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Ryuzaki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering where you two went. You came here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why does Yugi have the same crest as those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's obviously because he used that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Used that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used their card?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey! Let go of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Get... off...! Stop... it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Haga said, 'cause a' Exchange, they swapped their hand cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you didn't expect me to be able to use The Barrier of Orichalcos so easily, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made a grave miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come to regret ever handing me the Orichalcos Barrier card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As expected of the nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In just one turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you've utilized all of the powers of The Barrier of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Reincarnation of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reincarnation of the Dead allows one Monster in the Graveyard to return to the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return Guardian Grarl back to my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't want any Monsters to be sent to the Graveyard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I set a face-down card on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up next! A Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Swords of Sealing Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yugi can't attack in the next three turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His attacks are sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, this Rafael fella's really puttin' up a good fightin' 'gainst Yugi's attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon Catapult Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catapult Turtle's Effect works by sacrificing a Monster on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can inflict direct damage to your Life Points equivalent to half the sacrificed Monster's Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swords of Sealing Light can't interfere with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap Card! Sacrifice Limiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Sacrifice Limiter in play, each player can only sacrifice one Monster per turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this turn, since you've already sacrificed one Monster to Summon Catapult Turtle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are unable to tribute any more Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card! Nightmare Binding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nightmare Binding... It deducts 800 points off the ATK of a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And adds that 800 points to my Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, the targeted Monster cannot be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't use Kuribabylon as a sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't change the fact that I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use Catapult Turtle to launch Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Black Magician is now in the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl's Attack Points will go up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rafael?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next turn, with just one more attack, your Life Points will be completely drained!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a reverse card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we settle this, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Black Magician Girl as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that, Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten the promise you've made with Black Magician Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, Shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using that Magic Card to decrease the impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now your Life Points are lower than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Swords of Sealing Light will expire this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next turn, Catapult Turtle will sacrifice itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your Life will become 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious that Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s gonna win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yugi for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person isn't Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrificing your Monsters one by one for the sake of winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A True Duelist wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness inside his heart is becoming stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to {\i1}win{\i0}, {\i1}don't{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who is it, or whatever means it may take...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sight, Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about\N your impending victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've proven well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've proven that darkness exists in {\i1}your{\i0} heart as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eagerness to win has caused you to fall into this trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos is a card whereby
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stronger the darkness in your heart is, the more power you can get from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully at what's on your field!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:14:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your persistence to win has turned these lovely Monsters ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a slave for more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done to the Monsters...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You activated The Barrier of Orichalcos, sealing away the power of Timaeus with your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary power in the world of Duel Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't even know that what I feared was that very power of the Legendary Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fates will depend on what I draw this round!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're finally in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment Magic! Sacred Sword of Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Guardian Eatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's the aura who's been protecting him all this time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Effect of Guardian Eatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul of the Sacred Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Effect of Guardian Eatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It removes from play every Monster in the opponent's Graveyard, and she will absorb their combined Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shall be Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second card is Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third is Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth is Illusion Beast Gazelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fifth one is Berfomet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done to these Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in your heart has sent these Monsters to their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stare at me with those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness in your heart has enabled Eatos to reach her full potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Attack Power is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear the wrath of these Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Eatos attacks!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gospel of Truth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost the most important thing in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall now become an offering for the revival of our God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, with this..!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, Other... Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...defeated...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return in good time to take {\i1}your{\i0} soul as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip on yourself, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're conscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, I was so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not "alright"...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my stead, Partner has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's soul got sealed was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.64,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yugi that always emerges victorious regardless of how tough it may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He actually got defeated, I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other Yugi is suffering from the loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the only one who can stop Doma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get back the soul of our usual Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stand up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, "The Torn Soul"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
